    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen is equipped with the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission, delivering torque through a factory M-variable differential lock. The chassis has undergone preventative subframe reinforcement, and the suspension retains its original geometry with fresh bushings throughout. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple with no bolster wear. Service records confirm recent valve lash adjustments and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the mechanical integrity is as pristine as the aesthetic. A truly turn-key enthusiast investment.",
